{{>layout/header}}
<link href="/css/dropdown.css" rel="stylesheet" />
<link href="/css/chat.css" rel="stylesheet" />
<div class="chatBox" style="width: 700px; height: 520px;">
    <div class="ttt" style="width: 320px; height: 40px;">
        <div class="dropdown" style="display: inline-block;">
            <button class="btn" type="button" id="dropdownMenuButton1" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false">
                ☰
            </button>
            <ul class="dropdown-menu" aria-labelledby="dropdownMenuButton1">
                <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#">리뷰쓰기</a></li>
                {{#owner}}
                <li class="dropdown-submenu"><a class="dropdown-item" tabindex="-1" href="#" id="statusDropdown" value="{{post.status}}">거래상태</a>
                    <input type="hidden" id="status" value="{{post.status}}">
                    <input type="hidden" id="postNo" value="{{post.id}}">
                    <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                        <li><a class="dropdown-item" tabindex="-1" href="#" onclick="setStandby()">거래대기</a></li>
                        <li><a class="dropdown-item" tabindex="-1" href="#" onclick="setProgress()">거래중</a></li>
                        <li><a class="dropdown-item" tabindex="-1" href="#" onclick="setDone()">거래완료</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                {{/owner}}
                <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#" onclick="chatOut()" style="color: red;">채팅창 나가기</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="title" style="display: inline-block;">{{post.title}}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="chatBoxTheme hhh" id="chatBoxTheme" style="width: 320px; height: 480px;">
        <div id="chatting" class="chatting" onchange="readCheck()"></div>

        <input type="hidden" id="sessionId" name="sessionId" value="{{userInfo.id}}">
        <input type="hidden" id="roomId" name="roomId" value="{{roomId}}">
        <input type="hidden" id="userName" name="userName" value="{{userInfo.id}}">
        <input type="hidden" id="listener" name="listener" value="{{listener}}">

        <div class="sendForm">
            <input type="hidden" value="{{userInfo.id}}" id="sender" name="sender">
            <textarea id="message" class="sendMessage" placeholder="메시지를 입력하세요."></textarea>
            <div class="button" onclick="send()"><p>전송</p></div>
            <div class="clear"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="reviewBox" style="width: 320px; height: 480px;">
        <p>거래를 진행해 보세요!</p>
        <p>
            채팅 시 개인정보 유출에 유의해주세요!
            채팅 시 상대를 비하하는 언어는 삼가해주세요!<br>
            어길 시 이용에 제한이 있을 수 있습니다.
        </p>

        <form>
        {{#buyReview}}
            <p>구매를 완료하셨나요?<br>판매자를 평가해주세요!</p>
            <input type="hidden" id="no" name="no" value="{{review.no}}">
            <input type="hidden" id="id" name="id" value="{{review.id}}">
            <input type="hidden" id="position" name="position" value="{{review.position}}">
            <input type="number" id="score" name="score" value="3">
            <button class="btn btn-outline-primary" id="btn-setReview">확인</button>
        {{/buyReview}}
        </form>

        <form>
        {{#sellReview}}
            <p>판매를 완료하셨나요?<br>구매자를 평가해주세요!</p>
            <input type="hidden" id="no" name="no" value="{{review.no}}">
            <input type="hidden" id="id" name="id" value="{{review.id}}">
            <input type="hidden" id="position" name="position" value="{{review.position}}">
            <input type="number" id="score" name="score" value="3">
            <button class="btn btn-outline-primary" id="btn-setReview">확인</button>
        {{/sellReview}}
        </form>
    </div>
</div>
{{>layout/js}}
<script src="/js/post.js"></script>
<script src="/js/chat.js"></script>
</body>
</html>